    <h2 align="left"><a name="Top" href=""></a><img src="/content/dam/learning-teaching/programs/conference/conference_date_logo.png" alt="Faculty Conference logo" title="Ryerson Faculty Conference 2015, Thursday May 21, 2015"></h2> 
<h2>Tomorrow's Classroom</h2> 
<p>Our faculty conference theme - “Tomorrow’s Classroom” - provided faculty with the chance to share the theory and practice on the future of university teaching and learning, innovative new teaching styles, technologically enhanced learning, and evolving learning outcomes to engage and inspire the heterogeneity that is our twenty-first century learners.</p> 
<p><a href="https://survey.ryerson.ca/s?s=4406"><strong>Take our survey on the Faculty Conference</strong></a><br> </p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p>
    





</div>
